embeds.title: Medical Department Discord Rules
embeds.description:
[1]-> Don't harass, discriminate, or generally be rude to other users. Keep jokes at the expense of others to a minimum.

[2]-> Don't spam channels.

[3]-> Don't post offensive, derogatory, or NSFW content.

[4]-> Respect the high ranks, although if you feel they can do a better job please reccomend so in <#909962474365779968> or their superiors.

[5]-> Try to keep channel topics to their specific channels.
